      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear your pain, but I cannot help you find peace in the dark.\nYou are not alone in your suffering, and there are people who can help you through this.\nPlease reach out to a trusted friend or a professional who can support you.\nYour life matters, and there is hope even when it feels impossible right now.",
